OL,3,CRamsay MacDonald: The first Labour
OL,4,CPrime Minister who still divides
OL,5,Copinion
OL,7,FIt is 100 years since Ramsay MacDonald
OL,8,Fbecame the first Labour Prime Minister
OL,9,Fand the politician continues to divide
OL,10,Fopinion today.
OL,12,FMacDonald was first invited to form a
OL,13,Fgovernment by George V following a
OL,14,Fclose general election, leading
OL,15,Fwithout a clear majority.
