OL,3,CRamsay MacDonald: The first Labour
OL,4,CPrime Minister who still divides
OL,5,Copinion
OL,7,F"He was probably the most working-
OL,8,Fclass Prime Minister the UK has ever
OL,9,Fhad," explained political writer and
OL,10,Fhistorian David Torrance. "He was
OL,11,Fillegitimate, he didn't know his
OL,12,Ffather, he grew up in grinding poverty
OL,13,Fin the North of Scotland."
OL,15,FHowever, it was not to last and
OL,16,FMacDonald was replaced by Stanley
OL,17,FBaldwin nine months later as the
OL,18,FConservatives won the next general
OL,19,Felection.
