OL,3,CRamsay MacDonald: The first Labour
OL,4,CPrime Minister who still divides
OL,5,Copinion
OL,7,F"I remember my grandmother telling me
OL,8,Fthe songs: If it's Shinwell let him
OL,9,Fin, if it's MacDonald, kick his shin,"
OL,10,FMr Morris joked.
OL,12,FHe made another political comeback
OL,13,Fback home in Scotland but died in 1937.
OL,15,FThere has been little in the way of
OL,16,Fcelebrations for the centenary, on 22
OL,17,FJanuary, but the significance of the
OL,18,Fmoment has not been underplayed.
