OL,7,F"I think it's a hugely significant
OL,8,Fanniversary," Mr Torrance said. "The
OL,9,Fadvent of the first Labour government
OL,10,Festablished the two-party system which
OL,11,Fstill exists in the United Kingdom to
OL,12,Fthis day.
