OL,3,CRamsay MacDonald: The first Labour
OL,4,CPrime Minister who still divides
OL,5,Copinion
OL,7,F"Without that first minority Labour
OL,8,Fgovernment, you wouldn't have had, or
OL,9,Fperhaps as soon as we did - the
OL,10,Fmajority governments of Clement
OL,11,FAttlee, Harold Wilson and Tony Blair."
OL,12,FSir Keir Starmer will hope to be the
OL,13,Flatest Labour leader to follow in
OL,14,FMacDonald's footsteps in the General
OL,15,FElection expected later this year.
